    public static class ForgeGuiFactory.ForgeConfigGui.VersionCheckEntry
extends GuiConfigEntries.CategoryEntry
    This custom list entry provides the Forge Version Checking Config entry on the Minecraft Forge Configuration screen. It extends the base Category entry class and defines the IConfigElement objects that will be used to build the child screen.
